667→     * I2C-based BQ24297 calls (AutoSetILim, SetPowerMode) are only done during
668→     * initial configuration in BQ24297_Config_Settings() to avoid I2C bus hangs.
669→     *
670→     * Charging is configured once at startup. The BQ24297 handles charging
671→     * autonomously based on its hardware configuration.
672→     */
673→
674→    /* Nothing to do here anymore - status updates happen in Power_UpdateStatusFromGPIO()
675→     * and BQ24297 configuration happens once at init */
676→}
